<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَيُّ الناسِ هُوَ؛ نَقَلَه الجوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">ويُرْوى:</span> أَيُّ <span class="c3">{الدَّهْداءِ هُوَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ الأعْرابيِّ:</span> يقالُ فِي زَجْرِ الإِبِلِ: دُهْ دُهْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وأَمَّا قَوْلُهم:</span>} دُهْ دُرَّيْن سَعْدَ القَيْنِ، فتقدَّمَ ذِكْرُه فِي الراءِ وَفِي النونِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[دوه]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>: <span class="c2">( {التَّدَوُّهُ)</span> :<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(أَهْمَلَهُ الجوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ الصَّاغانيُّ:</span> هُوَ (التَّغَيُّرُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>(و) أَيْضاً: <span class="c2">(التَقَحُّمُ)</span> فِي الأُمُورِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(} ودَوْهُ)</span> ، بضمِّ الهاءِ، وبخطِّ الصَّاغانيّ بكسْرِها، <span class="c2">(ويُضَمُّ)</span> أَي أَوَّلُه: <span class="c2">(دُعاءٌ للرُّبَعِ)</span> ، كصُرَدٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">( <span class="c3">{والتَّدْوِيهُ: أَن تَدْعُوَ الإِبِلَ فتقولَ:}</span> داهْ <span class="c3">{داهْ بالكسْرِ والتّسْكِينِ، أَوْ}</span> دُهْ {دُهْ، بالضَّمِّ، لتَجِيءَ إِلَى وَلَدِها)</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(وممَّا يُسْتدركُ عَلَيْهِ:<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">} دَاهَ {دَوْهاً:</span> إِذا تَحَيَّرَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>(فصل الذَّال) مَعَ الْهَاء)<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَهْمَلَهُ الجَوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[ذمه]</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>: <span class="c2">(ذَمِهَ الحَرُّ،<span class="c5"> كفَرِحَ:</span> اشْتَدَّ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>(و) ذَمِهَ <span class="c2">(الرُّجلُ بالحَرِّ: اشْتَدَّ عَلَيْهِ)</span> وأَلِمَ دِماغُه مِنْهُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">(والمعجمةُ لُغَةٌ فِي جَميعِ مَعانِي المهْملَةِ)</span> .<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c2">(وممَّا يُسْتدركُ عَلَيْهِ:<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">أَذْمَهَتْه الشَّمسُ:</span> آلَمَتْ دِماغَه.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وذَمِهَ يومُنا،<span class="c5"> كفَرِحَ ونَصَرَ:</span> اشْتَدَّ حَرُّه.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
