<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c2">(أَهْمَلَهُ الجوْهرِيُّ وصاحِبُ اللِّسانِ.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
